All Implemented Interfaces:
Savable
public class MessageLoader extends YamlUtils implements Savable
The MessageLoader class extends YamlUtils and implements Savable to manage message configurations. This class is responsible for loading and saving custom messages to a YAML file for a Bukkit plugin.
